attributes.action: Urge the United Nations to provide search and rescue teams to Ukraine urgently
attributes.additional_details: This is something that needs to be addressed at the global stage in a way only the UK Government can do. As a country supporting Ukraine, we need to support them in holding the United Nations to account publicly and urgently so Ukraine can receive the vital search and rescue teams along with the vital aid needed to prevent further far reaching consequences and preserve life of both humans and the ecological system.
attributes.background: Urge the United Nations to urgently provide Ukraine with the search and rescue teams along with vital aid needed to support after the horrific Kakhovka dam collapse.
